			"fontSize": 12,
			"fontFamily": 1,
			"text": "BaseService (核心业务类)\nbase_service_utils.py (1485行)\n────────────────────────────────\n────\n属性:\n  - owner: str\n  - project_name: str\n  - test_request_name: str\n  - inherited_factory_contact_name: str\n  - plm_client: PLMClient\n  - ftp_client: FTPClient\n  - test_request_data: dict\n  - inherited_factory_contact_data: dict\n  - ldap_data: dict\n  - svn_software_address: str\n────────────────────────────────\n────\n项目验证方法:\n  + is_project_exist() -> bool\n  + inquire_request_exist_contact_letter() -> dict\n  + inquire_series_exist_contact_letter() -> dict\n  + inquire_latest_test_request() -> str\n────────────────────────────────\n────\n数据初始化方法:\n  + init_test_request_data() -> None\n  + init_contact_letter_data() -> None\n  + init_version_access_path_file_list() -> None\n────────────────────────────────\n────\nSVN路径生成:\n  + generate_svn_software_address() -> str\n  + get_v_part_number() -> str\n  + get_product_brand() -> str\n────────────────────────────────\n────\n数据获取方法 (80+个getter):\n  + get_test_request_version() -> str\n  + get_market() -> str\n  + get_chip() -> str\n  + get_emmc_file_name() -> str\n  + get_ota_file_name() -> str\n  + get_mboot_file_name() -> str\n  + get_usb_file_name() -> str\n  ... (85个字段)",
			"textAlign": "left",
			"verticalAlign": "top",
			"containerId": "class-baseService",
			"originalText": "BaseService (核心业务类)\nbase_service_utils.py (1485行)\n────────────────────────────────\n────\n属性:\n  - owner: str\n  - project_name: str\n  - test_request_name: str\n  - inherited_factory_contact_name: str\n  - plm_client: PLMClient\n  - ftp_client: FTPClient\n  - test_request_data: dict\n  - inherited_factory_contact_data: dict\n  - ldap_data: dict\n  - svn_software_address: str\n────────────────────────────────\n────\n项目验证方法:\n  + is_project_exist() -> bool\n  + inquire_request_exist_contact_letter() -> dict\n  + inquire_series_exist_contact_letter() -> dict\n  + inquire_latest_test_request() -> str\n────────────────────────────────\n────\n数据初始化方法:\n  + init_test_request_data() -> None\n  + init_contact_letter_data() -> None\n  + init_version_access_path_file_list() -> None\n────────────────────────────────\n────\nSVN路径生成:\n  + generate_svn_software_address() -> str\n  + get_v_part_number() -> str\n  + get_product_brand() -> str\n────────────────────────────────\n────\n数据获取方法 (80+个getter):\n  + get_test_request_version() -> str\n  + get_market() -> str\n  + get_chip() -> str\n  + get_emmc_file_name() -> str\n  + get_ota_file_name() -> str\n  + get_mboot_file_name() -> str\n  + get_usb_file_name() -> str\n  ... (85个字段)",
